dc_title_s: Offfshore Wind Speed 90-Meters, Atlantic Coast, United States, 2011
dc_description_s: This raster data layer contains the annual average offshore wind speed for the Atlantic Coast (Connecticut, Delaware, Georgia, Massachusetts, Maine, Maryland, New Hampshire, New Jersey, New York, North Carolina, Rhode Island, South Carolina, and Virginia) at a 90 meter height.These data provide information on the wind resource development potential for the Atlantic Coast.
